More Service Cloud Features

Customer Service Incident Management must be enabled.
Broadcast Slack messages must be enabled.
Broadcast topics must be assigned to Slack channels.

To delete a broadcast Slack message:
Find the Broadcast Communications related list on the incident related lists.
Select Delete Broadcast Slack Message from the dropdown.
Click Next, and then Done.
title: Deleting a Broadcast Slack Message in Service Cloud
